v class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-dining-at-kandolhu\">Dining at Kandolhu<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The small island offers a wide range of dining from Japanese Teppanyaki, fresh sea grill, Mediterranean and more. At The Market, there is a daily breakfast and lunch. You will be having breakfast with a beautiful ocean view. With just 30 rooms on the island, you don&#x2019;t have to worry about restaurants being too crowded.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/kandolhu-island-maldives-dining.jpg\" alt=\"kandolhu island maldives dining\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"323\" alt=\"kandolhu island maldives dining\" class=\"wp-image-8320 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152528\/kandolhu-island-maldives-dining.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152528\/kandolhu-island-maldives-dining-300x215.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152528\/kandolhu-island-maldives-dining-600x431.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152528\/kandolhu-island-maldives-dining-450x323.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152528\/kandolhu-island-maldives-dining-800x575.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152528\/kandolhu-island-maldives-dining-1080x776.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152528\/kandolhu-island-maldives-dining-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152528\/kandolhu-island-maldives-dining-163x117.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/23152528\/kandolhu-island-maldives